      <intermediateExchange id="a9a616d1-bee1-563c-82f7-863f124aca33" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" amount="1.3980707690264E-05" intermediateExchangeId="4c2b1cc3-84e5-4e35-b74e-8815eadbc674" activityLinkId="db6536db-5f07-5bf0-9179-7419a6157c5a">
        <name xml:lang="en">[sulfonyl]urea-compound</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">This exchange is an aggregate of proxies for applied pesticide(s) SAFLUFENACIL, Halosulfuron-methyl, Tembotrione, Hexythiazox, Novaluron (2.222E-2 kg/ha {1,2,2,1,1}; 1.113E-1 kg/ha {1,2,2,1,1}; 3.038E-2 kg/ha {1,2,2,1,1}; 3.69E-2 kg/ha {1,2,2,1,1}; 3.428E-2 kg/ha {1,2,2,1,1}, respectively).
Data reported a quantity of total insecticides/herbicides/fungicides applied in sweet corn is sometimes available even when many of the substances in the category are reported with a “D”. If this total is available, the amount remaining after the sum of substance-specific values is accounted for is divided equally among the substances reported with a “D”. If the sum of available values exceeds or equals the total reported, any remaining “D” substances are treated as zero and omitted. 
From SWEETCORN - APPLICATIONS, MEASURED IN LB / ACRE / YEAR, AVG (fertilizer and pesticides, amount, number of applications) - 2000-2021, https://quickstats.nass.usda.gov/#5E5B411A-F9EF-3B83-AAFF-995DD89820FC</comment>
        <uncertainty>
          <normal meanValue="1.3980707690264E-05" variance="1.75429675586897E-13" varianceWithPedigreeUncertainty="1.75429675586897E-13"/>
          <pedigreeMatrix reliability="2" completeness="3" temporalCorrelation="3" geographicalCorrelation="3" furtherTechnologyCorrelation="1"/>
        </uncertainty>
        <property propertyId="f2283db2-62e4-467f-b9ac-c4f45be563b4" amount="0.540852630062696" isDefiningValue="false" isCalculatedAmount="false" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
          <name xml:lang="en">carbon allocation</name>
